      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal characterization of test sample variability is not required when a single representative device geometry is used.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on a single FDA benchmark pump specimen. Sample-to-sample variability assessment not required at MRL 2. Single-specimen approach accepted per MRL 2 scoping decision."
    },
